<script>
import { mapActions, mapState } from "vuex";

export default {
  name: "Cart",

  props: {
    cart: Object,
  },

  data() {
    return {
      currCart: null,
    };
  },

  computed: {
    ...mapState(["token", "currCart"]),
  },

  created: {},

  methods: {
    ...mapActions(["getToken", "getCart", "removeGameFromCart"]),
  },
  mounted() {},
};
</script>
